## ğŸ“Š Code Summary

```python
from sklearn.naive_bayes import GaussianNB
from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score

# Train the model
model = GaussianNB()
model.fit(x_train, y_train)

# Predict and evaluate
accuracy = accuracy_score(y_test, model.predict(x_test))
```

